{"tid":1721261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[推俾全世界] 黑警帶領黑幫於全港發動721式恐襲","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:06:53.000Z","uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"648a2adf135f64d58fc9aec31b6b9a844ec6d64c","tid":1721261,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"小弟不才 出唔到篇文去舉證說服俾大家share/睇<br />\n但請用任何文字 分析 描述 甚至外國文宣<br />\n將依個事實 訊息帶俾全世界 包括大部分人手持伸縮警棍<br />\n<br />\n警謊會話我地允許神獸 但黑衣人受襲就要求警曱拉人<br />\n依說法係一攻即破<br />\n1. 神獸係因為對方傷人/持武器傷人等原因 而警曱唔執法 反而包庇 先令到神獸倔起<br />\n2. 班人打&rdquo;黑衣人&rdquo;係冇原因 只係因為身穿黑衣/年輕 就成為目標被襲<br />\n3. 班施襲者係受支共 政權 警曱包庇 甚至帶領出嚟打人 無任何後果 而神獸係會被秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L7pn2hA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL7pn2hA.jpg&h=0c9ab673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎提供更多圖片/影像"},{"pid":"47405cd4b27b74c80e7e2362cde030f64bf11d00","tid":1721261,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856af7f9aaacf60588dc5c21d35e50c44c9cf721","tid":1721261,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:18:07.000Z","msg":"好似死咗圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TtnH5AF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtnH5AF.jpg&h=147d34a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1de2f38d23821d20b400f918556251e31eff089b","tid":1721261,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd361f156d424feab97326e9eb60c52fd502b23a","tid":1721261,"uid":171404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/px93P3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"